We are sorry, due to equipment failure beyond our control, all
communications have been down for some time, and scanners are still not
functioning properly. For anyone who is currently just outside the Pinch
Inc. Neutral Zone, we apologies for the inconvenience, and would like to ask
if anyone currently wishes entrance through the field for business reasons.
Thank you for your attention.
